Pre-Game Insights: Nagelsmann has the selection head-scratcher of deciding whether to start Florian Wirtz or Niclas Füllkrug, both of whom have performed exceptionally well in the tournament.
Füllkrug has scored three of Germany's eight goals, including the crucial injury-time equalizer against Switzerland.
Nagelsmann emphasized that his substitutes matter and they have thrived in various roles, contributing significantly to the team's success.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The mosquito outbreak infested the team's training camp.
Torrential weather is expected around game-time, including hailstones and lightning.
